synopsis: Three complete strangers were selected to compete in the Biz Game. The three of them don't get along at all, but have to work together to earn the prize of 1 billion dollars, which all three of them need.
Team AAA (No Name) won their first match. In the next match, they're the home team, and they have to plan and learn to co-operate if they have any hope of winning.

The final episode starts out with Team AAA (no name), going to the match location. It turns out the match is on a rooftop with a Hawaiian themed party going on. What's gonna be the outcome of the match for Team AAA (no name).
